MobileRecallCommentForm is a Form
    title is "Comment"
    Actions
        action is save
        action is previous record
        action is next record
        action is refresh
    Layout
        single column
            RecallNotice
                display as text
            RecallNotice.Name
                no label
                display as text
            Title
            Comment
                use text area of 5 lines
            CommentDate
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                Attachment.Title
            Attachment.File
                label is "Attachment"
